name: Ali Smith
summary: Ali Smith, a 31-year-old gay man, is a software engineer in the tech industry who originally hails from Chicago but is now located in Los Angeles. At Yale University, he completed his graduate studies. He is a Muslim with liberal political views, who speaks English and Arabic fluently. His values center around honesty, loyalty, and equality. Ali is actively ambitious; his hobbies include traveling, reading, and learning new languages. A Gemini with an INFJ personality type, he sometimes drinks but does not smoke or use recreational drugs. In terms of fitness, he maintains an active exercise routine. Ali doesn't have children but would like to in the future, and he has a pet dog. He is interested in a life partner who wants children, maintains an active lifestyle, and doesn't smoke or use recreational drugs. His preferred partner's age would range between 26 and 38.
